asset.hookText:
August the 23th- 26th, 2010, ZERO and the Norwegian Automobile- Sport Federation is organizing the 2010 ZeroEmission rally. The 700 km rally starts in Oslo and arrives in Stavanger at the Offshore Northern Sea conference (ONS 2010).

The rally runs along the Norwegian scenic coastline and interior and will test the performance of hydrogen, plug- in hybrid and battery electric cars.
